Class ListParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.icecave.dialekt.parser.AbstractParser

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserInterface

    public class ListParser
extends AbstractParser
    Parses a list of tags. The expression must be a space-separated list of tags. The result is either EmptyExpression, a single Tag node, or a LogicalAnd node containing only Tag nodes.
